{"tid":103473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]同女神食西餐撈亂左啲叉黎用，可以點樣不失霸氣？","createTime":"2017-02-01T11:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T13:04:40.000Z","uid":542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91503366dc67c6f46d5fb6033feef872a07c6cac","tid":103473,"uid":542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，琴日約左女神食西餐<br />\n見到張枱有三隻叉<br />\n咁我以為最細果隻係甜品用<br />\n中SIZE果隻係食前菜沙律<br />\n最大果隻係食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就拎左中SIZE果隻黎食沙律<br />\n點知女神同我講：咦，乜呢支叉唔係用黎食魚架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我吓左一聲唔識答，即刻柒撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前扮出黎果啲紳士氣息蕩然無存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返到屋企我諗左一日都諗唔到應該點樣優雅又不失霸氣地打圓場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特此上黎求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1r8D6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1r8D6Q.jpg&h=de6aa070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8d323f9aaaf1aea572f635b412c80c21cffcfed","tid":103473,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"你話：我知呀 不過依隻感覺食肉方便好多。你都試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5029a57d7a55d08983a21f3427ba6bb8543c44a9","tid":103473,"uid":67113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5d0a625874d82c35fda189fc9ff1a5a37caf11d","tid":103473,"uid":54076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"記住！由外食到內呀！"},{"pid":"8e176da2f2df3d5174ba7bab8f12f052af1261a1","tid":103473,"uid":542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:06:20.000Z","msg":"之前一直注意住各種細節<img src=\"/assets/fac